episodes.title: What the Epstein Files Reveal About America’s Elite
episodes.description: Millions of documents related to the Jeffrey Epstein case dropped... and it has sparked new questions, renewed scrutiny, and a political firestorm that reaches across party lines. Former Donald Trump attorney Christina Bobb joins Caitlin Sinclair on this episode to break down what was actually released on America's elite, why the timing matters, and how the fallout could affect both Republicans and Democrats. It’s sharp, unapologetic, and impossible to ignore. If you’ve felt like today’s conversations about the world have moved on without you, you’re in the right place — welcome to The Caitlin Sinclair Show.
